msgstr "清除边缘缓存"

msgid "Purging cache will temporarily slow down your site for all visitors while the cache rebuilds."
msgstr "清除缓存期间，网站对所有访客可能会暂时变慢。"

msgid "Settings to manage the object cache."
msgstr "用于管理对象缓存的设置。"

